cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.SD, cs.CL

The paper proposes a new algorithm for classification using clustering methods, which is a common topic in machine learning (cs.LG) and computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed algorithm also involves semi-supervised learning (cs.AI) and graph theory (cs.SD). Additionally, the paper evaluates the algorithm's performance on image-set classification datasets, which falls under natural language processing and computational linguistics (cs.CL).
